description: Qleanair Holding AB supplies premium solutions within the air cleaning market for indoor environments. The company is headquartered in Solna, Stockholm and currently employs 106 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2019-12-12. Its offering consists of long-term full-service contracts encompassing clean air technology, hardware solutions, installation and maintenance. The Company’s technology platform, with proprietary filters and back-office technology, enable a differentiated portfolio of turn-key products, such as smoking cabins, air cleaner for different kind of facilities and solutions for clean and sterile environments. The firm addresses the need of a variety of customers, including workspaces, public spaces, industries and cleanrooms. The company is active globally.
naics: Management, Scientific, and Technical Consulting Services
name: Qleanair Holding AB
